original_title: Het Zwanenmeer - Ballet van de Staatsopera Bulgarije
overview: With impressive sets and dazzling costumes, this fairytale ballet tells the love story of Prince Siegfried and Odette, a beautiful princess who has been kidnapped by a wizard and turned into a queen swan. With beautiful choreography by Marius Petipa to the beautiful music of Tchaikovsky. Enchanting for young and old!
title: Het Zwanenmeer - Ballet van de Staatsopera Bulgarije
